FAQ
1. What is checked?

  • If all RELATED IMAGES defined in the CSV are using SHA
  • If the CSV has the labels with all architectures found by inspecting the images
  • If the CSV has the the annotation: `operators.openshift.io/infrastructure-features:disconnected`
  • If all install images and related images are with all supported architectures found`
